title: Sidebar-Menu
description: Use the sidebar menu to navigate through the analyses

title: Data Bank
description: Use the Data Bank menu to create and inspect Datalists

title: Create Datalist
description: iMESC requires at least one datalist to open the analysis panels. Use this button to create datalists using the upload dialog panel.

title: Upload Dialog
description: This is the upload dialog for creating Datalists...

title: Upload
description: If you choose upload you must upload at least two files: Data-Attribute and Factor-Attribute

title: Example data
description: In this tutorial we create a Datalist using the example data option
